====== Simon Riggs ======

Simon has been a PostgreSQL Major Developer since release 8.0 and is liked and trusted throughout the Postgres community. He has also worked extensively with Teradata, Oracle and DB2 and has been responsible for RDBMS selection at a number of major companies. He has a crystal ball.

===== PostgreSQL: The Next 20 Years =====

A look at the things we need to do in the next 20 years to continue to provide a relevant, cutting edge solution to the world's data problems. We'll look back over the last 20 years of our own development, as well as looking at what has happened in academia and industry over the same period and where things are going now.  Where next? Come and see.


